  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/d189a10a328257443a4e51a789e88040.avif?t=1729153469\" width=542 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All owners of Flying Red Barrel - The Diary of a Little Aviator will unlock a free bonus character in <strong>100% Orange Juice</strong> on Steam.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/0a4218d90f4138506a925511be9f55e5.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/0a4218d90f4138506a925511be9f55e5.webm?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/0a4218d90f4138506a925511be9f55e5.mp4?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>\"People flying in the air? What baloney! If God had meant man to fly, He would have given him wings.\"</i><br><br>As though no such thing had ever been uttered, mankind has now gained its wings.<br><br>What people dreamed of as children is the reality of today.<br><br>Everyone reaches out for the sky together, carrying their wishes upon their wings. <br><br>With the rapid development of flight technology, an organization called the \"Blue Sky Union\" was established to maintain the order of the sky under law. People now call it \"the Guild.\"<br><br>Ten years have passed since, and the Guild is at last about to put an end to the prolonged anarchy of the sky.<br><br>This is a story of one of the aviators living in that era.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/bb75afdc1851d5d7c1b5c88167e4f96f.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/bb75afdc1851d5d7c1b5c88167e4f96f.webm?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/bb75afdc1851d5d7c1b5c88167e4f96f.mp4?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Flying Red Barrel ~The Diary of a Little Aviator~ is an old-school bullet hell/STG game with multiple endings based on actions you take.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/f92fe5016cf98c349b95209d8a853f72.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/f92fe5016cf98c349b95209d8a853f72.webm?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/f92fe5016cf98c349b95209d8a853f72.mp4?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 challenging stages<br></li><li>3 difficulty settings<br></li><li>Secret bosses<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>An advanced scoring system</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/07293db13837a0a1c187b97070ff332e.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/07293db13837a0a1c187b97070ff332e.webm?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/07293db13837a0a1c187b97070ff332e.mp4?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Steam version has been remastered to 1280x960 resolution.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/cc472e196922b4dff55dcfea96fea23a.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/cc472e196922b4dff55dcfea96fea23a.webm?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/cc472e196922b4dff55dcfea96fea23a.mp4?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/0a4218d90f4138506a925511be9f55e5.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/0a4218d90f4138506a925511be9f55e5.webm?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/0a4218d90f4138506a925511be9f55e5.mp4?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>\"People flying in the air? What baloney! If God had meant man to fly, He would have given him wings.\"</i><br><br>As though no such thing had ever been uttered, mankind has now gained its wings.<br><br>What people dreamed of as children is the reality of today.<br><br>Everyone reaches out for the sky together, carrying their wishes upon their wings. <br><br>With the rapid development of flight technology, an organization called the \"Blue Sky Union\" was established to maintain the order of the sky under law. People now call it \"the Guild.\"<br><br>Ten years have passed since, and the Guild is at last about to put an end to the prolonged anarchy of the sky.<br><br>This is a story of one of the aviators living in that era.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/bb75afdc1851d5d7c1b5c88167e4f96f.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/bb75afdc1851d5d7c1b5c88167e4f96f.webm?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/bb75afdc1851d5d7c1b5c88167e4f96f.mp4?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Flying Red Barrel ~The Diary of a Little Aviator~ is an old-school bullet hell/STG game with multiple endings based on actions you take.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/f92fe5016cf98c349b95209d8a853f72.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/f92fe5016cf98c349b95209d8a853f72.webm?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/f92fe5016cf98c349b95209d8a853f72.mp4?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 challenging stages<br></li><li>3 difficulty settings<br></li><li>Secret bosses<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>An advanced scoring system</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/07293db13837a0a1c187b97070ff332e.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/07293db13837a0a1c187b97070ff332e.webm?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/07293db13837a0a1c187b97070ff332e.mp4?t=1729153469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Steam version has been remastered to 1280x960 resolution.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036370/extras/cc472e196922b4dff55dcfea96fea23a.poster.avif?t=1729153469\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c